src:
Hasil FP1 Moto3 Malaysia: Andrea Migno Catat Waktu Tercepat
01 Nov 2019, 09:10 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap Mugen Race, Andrea Migno, sukses mencatatkan waktu tercepat dalam sesi latihan bebas pertama (FP1) Moto3 Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Jumat (1/11/2019).
Pebalap Italia ini diikuti oleh pebalap Sterilgarda Max Racing Team, Aron Canet, di posisi kedua, dan pebalap Leopard Racing, Lorenzo dalla Porta, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap VNE Snipers Team, Tony Arbolino, dan pebalap Mugen Race lainnya, Jaume Masia.
Berikut hasil FP1 Moto3 Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian Moto3 FP1 Results: Andrea Migno Record the Fastest Time
Nov 1 2019, 09:10 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Mugen Race driver Andrea Migno successfully recorded the fastest time in the first free practice session (FP1) of Moto3 Malaysia at the Sepang Circuit on Friday (11/01/2019).
The Italian rider was followed by Sterilgarda Max Racing Team, Aron Canet, in second place, and Leopard Racing driver Lorenzo dalla Porta in third.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by VNE Snipers Team rider Tony Arbolino and Mugen Race racer Jaume Masia.
Following are the results of FP1 Moto3 Malaysia 2019.
